### Listar responsáveis
GET http://localhost:3002/responsaveis

### Buscar responsável por id
GET http://localhost:3002/responsaveis/1

### Criar responsável
POST http://localhost:3002/responsaveis
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria Silva",
  "telefone": "(11) 99999-9999"
}

### Atualizar responsável
PUT http://localhost:3002/responsaveis/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "telefone": "(11) 98888-8888"
}

### Deletar responsável
DELETE http://localhost:3002/responsaveis/1
